Another_Woman http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Another_Woman 0 Another Woman is a 1988 American drama film written and directed by Woody Allen. It stars Gena Rowlands as a philosophy professor who accidentally overhears the private analysis of a stranger, and finds the woman's regrets and despair awaken something personal in her. Another Woman is viewed favorably by modern film critics. Another Woman is a 1988 American drama film written and directed by Woody Allen. Another Woman is viewed favorably by modern film critics.
